<h1>L3 - On-Campus Informal</h1>
<p><img alt="l3 digital postcard screenshot" height="133" src="Images/university-communications/digital_postcard_l3.jpg" title="L3 Digital Postcard" width="200" /></p>
<h2>Description:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Most common level of university communication</li>
<li>Requires least amount of branding elements</li>
<li>Reserved for on-campus communication</li>
</ul>
<h2>Who:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Anyone advertising an informal event on-campus</li>
</ul>
<h2>Examples:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Society event</li>
<li>Department of Music recitals</li>
<li>Activities and Academic Department sponsored events</li>
</ul>
