<h1>L2-University Semi-Formal</h1>
<p><img alt="l2 digital postcard screenshot" height="133" src="Images/university-communications/digital_postcard_l2.jpg" title="L2 Digital Postcard" width="200" /></p>
<h2>Description:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Used for communications that are tied to the <a href="http://www2.byui.edu/identity/brand/discipleleadermodel.htm">core foundation values</a></li>
<li>Used for guest speaking events, touring groups and other off campus events that are semi-formal in nature.</li>
<li>More formal in nature than Level 3 events, but less formal than Level 1 events</li>
</ul>
<h2>Who:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Reserved specifically for touring group and forum use</li>
</ul>
<h2>Examples:</h2>
<ul>
<li>University forums and Entrepreneur Conference</li>
</ul>
