<h1>L1-University Formal</h1>
<p><img alt="l1 digital postcard screenshot" height="133" src="Images/university-communications/digital_postcard_l1.jpg" title="L1 Digital Postcard" width="200" /></p>
<h2>Description:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Reserved for official university messages</li>
<li>Messages are formal in nature</li>
<li>Used most often for off-campus formal communication</li>
</ul>
<h2>Who:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Departments, colleges, and offices wishing to communicate fundamental messages on and off campus</li>
</ul>
<h2>Examples:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Executive Office, or to be displayed in Institute buildings</li>
</ul>
